how long lived the king ? in kmt vol 22 , n 2 , summer 2010   modern interest in akhenaten and his queen , nefertiti , comes partly from his connection with tutankhamun , partly from the unique style and high quality of the pictorial arts he patronized , and partly from ongoing interest in the religion he attempted to establish .

